Attributions
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Portions of the analytical methodology in `.claude/skills/` (the peer-comparison
quality discipline, the due-diligence severity taxonomy, and the screening-verdict
framing) are adapted from Anthropic's public reference implementation for
financial-services agents:

    anthropics/financial-services
    https://github.com/anthropics/financial-services
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0

These are adaptations for a local Indian-equities data lake, not verbatim copies.

